  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à At-Spi2 Core</title>

    <para>
      The <application>At-Spi2 Core</application> package contains a comprehensive
accessibility framework for the Assistive Technologies available on the
<application>GNOME</application> platform. This includes a set of interfaces
which are implemented by other toolkits and applications.
    </para>

    &lfs112_checked;

